 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "intro",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# ☁️ Day 8: GCP + Your First Cloud Deployment\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal:** Deploy a Python app to Google Cloud Run!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "check-gcloud",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 1. Check gcloud CLI"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "check-gcloud-code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Check if gcloud is installed\n",
    "!gcloud --version"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "flask-app",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 2. Create Simple Flask App"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "flask-code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Create the Flask app\n",
    "flask_app_code = '''\n",
    "from flask import Flask, jsonify\n",
    "\n",
    "app = Flask(__name__)\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.route('/')\n",
    "def hello():\n",
    "    return jsonify({\n",
    "        \"message\": \"Hello from Cloud Run!\",\n",
    "        \"status\": \"deployed\",\n",
    "        \"platform\": \"Google Cloud Run\"\n",
    "    })\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.route('/health')\n",
    "def health():\n",
    "    return jsonify({\"status\": \"healthy\"})\n",
    "\n",
    "if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n",
    "    app.run(host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=8080)\n",
    "'''\n",
    "\n",
    "with open('main.py', 'w') as f:\n",
    "    f.write(flask_app_code)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ main.py created!\")\n",
    "print(\"\\n--- main.py ---\")\n",
    "print(flask_app_code)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "dockerfile",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 3. Create Dockerfile"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "dockerfile-code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Create Dockerfile\n",
    "dockerfile_content = '''\n",
    "# Use official Python runtime\n",
    "FROM python:3.11-slim\n",
    "\n",
    "# Set working directory\n",
    "WORKDIR /app\n",
    "\n",
    "# Copy files\n",
    "COPY . .\n",
    "\n",
    "# Install Flask\n",
    "RUN pip install flask gunicorn\n",
    "\n",
    "# Expose port\n",
    "EXPOSE 8080\n",
    "\n",
    "# Run with gunicorn (production)\n",
    "CMD [\"gunicorn\", \"--bind\", \"0.0.0.0:8080\", \"main:app\"]\n",
    "'''\n",
    "\n",
    "with open('Dockerfile', 'w') as f:\n",
    "    f.write(dockerfile_content)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ Dockerfile created!\")\n",
    "print(\"\\n--- Dockerfile ---\")\n",
    "print(dockerfile_content)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "test-local",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 4. Test Locally (Optional)"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "test-local-code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Test the app locally\n",
    "print(\"To test locally:\")\n",
    "print(\"1. pip install flask gunicorn\")\n",
    "print(\"2. python main.py\")\n",
    "print(\"3. Visit http://localhost:8080\")\n",
    "print(\"\\n✅ App is ready for deployment!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "deploy",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 5. Deploy to Cloud Run"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "deploy-code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Commands to deploy (run in terminal)\n",
    "deploy_commands = '''\n",
    "# 1. Authenticate\n",
    "gcloud auth login\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. Set project\n",
    "gcloud config set project YOUR_PROJECT_ID\n",
    "\n",
    "# 3. Enable Cloud Run API\n",
    "gcloud services enable run.googleapis.com\n",
    "\n",
    "# 4. Deploy!\n",
    "gcloud run deploy my-flask-app \\\n",
    "    --source . \\\n",
    "    --region us-central1 \\\n",
    "    --allow-unauthenticated\n",
    "'''\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🚀 Deploy Commands:\")\n",
    "print(deploy_commands)\n",
    "print(\"\\nAfter deployment, you'll get a URL like:\")\n",
    "print(\"https://my-flask-app-xyz.a.run.app\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "checkpoint",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## ✅ Today's Checkpoint\n",
    "\n",
    "- [ ] Understand GCP basics (project, region, zone)\n",
    "- [ ] Create Flask app\n",
    "- [ ] Create Dockerfile\n",
    "- [ ] Deploy to Cloud Run\n",
    "- [ ] Visit your live endpoint!"
  }
